dc:description: Greenish blue glass.  Rim appears to have been cut off.  Milky weathering.  Somewhat iridescent.  Frosting.  Material good.  A few bubbles.  Toilet bottle.  What remains of the neck has a constriction at its base and swelling at its mid point.  Oval body.  Slightly concave base.
Gazda: Toilet bottle. Glass, free blown.
